Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 莲治君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 今天好像很悠闲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给 我把小说写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结局由我自己完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这… 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你完成小说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样还不算完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后在莲治君读后 没有异议才算完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为它是我和莲治君共同创作的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结局你选了哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是女孩走入画中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抑或是男孩从画中走出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时还没决定要选哪个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于那个… 你读后就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等我回去后再读
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得向你道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道谢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅凭我一己之力是无法完成小说的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都多亏了莲治君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千寻本来就有写作方面的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 倘若没有莲治君的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大概什么都不会做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莲治君为我创造了实现唯一梦想的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对… 这样一来我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请务必接受我的谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很感谢莲治君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千寻…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么我能做的 请尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你愿意和我约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约会… 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约会是情侣间的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能… 成为情侣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 我果然不够格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不会呢 不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们做情侣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过仅限一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅限一天？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:03:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和莲治君明天就做一天的情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有明天一天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就当是试恋期好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那… 后天开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些明天再考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那本小说… 你能下次再读吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请在明天约会后再读
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:30.15,BIGSUB,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(651,368)\fs51\fn方正隶变_GBK\1c&H000000}瞬间{\1c&HFFFFFF}的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们还真像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说我和谁很像？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道… 我已经忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是火村先生在等待的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓喜欢上一个人 是种怎样的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 无可救药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无可救药？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你察觉到 为时已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管个人感情如何 都已经迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么说来 我可能已经无可救药了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 承蒙您常年关照 十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 说得这么一本正经的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无意间就脱口而出了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想说时不说的话 我会忘掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和莲治君说得一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这个交给他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是某种风俗罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早… 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这身衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是约会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就稍稍打扮了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐买给我的 还从没穿过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮 很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想先看场电影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看什么类型的好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候果然要看爱情片？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要不悲伤就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不悲伤的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能会簌簌掉泪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那喜剧怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我没想到结局会变成那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真败了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起… 离开下… 心情有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要纸巾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身上有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过真是个好故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剧情有些出人意料 很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起初还以为纯属闹剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到却这么动人心弦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到剧情最后急转直下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后是大团圆结局 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的… 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去洗个脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要纸巾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真坏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想必不太喜欢人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏厅就不考虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是有点难
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械臂弹簧强度不够
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娃娃材质又滑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旁边那个兔子倒是很好抓的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 下次给你买个一样的好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道哪里有卖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们视线交汇了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说了「请带我走」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就要那个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定给你抓上来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定… 一定… 一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别松手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样… 就这样… 就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小啾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小啾？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家里那个是小叽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而这个是小啾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这… 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:08:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请给我一张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一人一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一张就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 莲治君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天玩得好尽兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 莲治君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能和你牵手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是情侣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有莲治君在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就像平常一样放松下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在要去做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话去海边好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海边？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说情侣都要去海边的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,书里是这么写的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情侣们来了这里要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两人就这么静静地坐着也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们之前也有来过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了… 很多很多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我读过日记 略知一二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事到了明天也肯定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天不要来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天可能会比今天更美好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差点被我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火村先生让我把这个送你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是学校楼顶的副钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚从楼顶眺望城市 景色非常之美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是指那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火村先生怎么会有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道… 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还真是个充满谜团的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那所学校有把钥匙代代相传的风俗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎… 我们去试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过后一定要谢谢火村先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑得太靠边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真得好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 直到明天 后天 永远
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远都喜欢千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太适合说这种话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说早就想说说看…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吻你么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接吻是只有情侣间才能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是千寻的恋人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候只要默默吻过来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰到牙齿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱… 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有点得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我好不容易才走到这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再把我拒于千里之外了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千寻…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和莲治君做真正的情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千寻呢 为什么要选我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也好喜欢莲治君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千寻…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莲治君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等… 等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是刚才的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么写的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能对人说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就只说能说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那… 碰到牙齿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实… 不能再多说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚十点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早九点与千寻在车站的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始每过一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天所发生的事情就会消失一小时份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 莲治君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试恋期过去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你带来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请读读看吧 这样才算完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千寻？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当面读的话我会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去楼顶读这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又想重温与莲治君相逢至今的种种了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,读完小说叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
