Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:15.44,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:18.68,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:25.01,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, with my little wings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:31.46,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back to the sorrow I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:37.55,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my real intention I hide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:44.27,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were here, and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:51.03,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:56.86,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been looking for my own style
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:01:03.87,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it up, here comes the life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.79,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Be alive, take it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:13.05,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise to find, yes I will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:19.43,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining wings filled with wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:22.64,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:25.89,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:32.69,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, so I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 凭借自己那小小的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫回首 将悲伤留在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我的真意所在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿君伴我身侧 与我肩并肩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚强地包容我的自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在为自己的风格而上下求索
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:01:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫轻言弃 这才是生命的真义所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 莫放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信 自己必会得到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那满怀希望 熠熠生辉的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 我坚信
